&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Provide timely and relevant strategic advice to clients informed by broad intelligence-gathering on client, sector and competitors and policy environment&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Project manage and supervise the delivery of all client services across multiple accounts&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Exhibit a willingness to challenge the status quo, innovate, and embrace new ideas to drive the business forward&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Lead regular client meetings and internal account management meetings, reviewing progress and allocating tasks&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Manage account teams, providing direction and support to ensure high-quality client service&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Manage client budgets and adhere to company budget setting and management processes&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ensure timely and accurate billing to ensure client needs are met within budget&lt;/li&gt;
